a giraffe, right?

261
00:12:48,235 --> 00:12:49,570
Emma: I said that?

262
00:12:49,603 --> 00:12:53,207
I guess I don’t really
want to leave,

263
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:55,008
so i’d stay forever.

264
00:12:55,042 --> 00:12:57,244
don: Come on.
