266
00:13:00,547 --> 00:13:02,649
Ray: Happy? Yeah.

267
00:13:02,683 --> 00:13:04,652
Conny: I promise
to write to you.

268
00:13:04,685 --> 00:13:06,520
I’ll write you
stacks of letters!

269
00:13:06,553 --> 00:13:09,256
