366
00:19:12,686 --> 00:19:14,154
( Norman panting )

367
00:19:14,188 --> 00:19:15,656
Emma: It can’t be.

368
00:19:15,689 --> 00:19:18,725
Didn’t everyone go
to foster homes?

369
00:19:18,759 --> 00:19:23,163
