372
00:19:39,079 --> 00:19:40,814
Norman: I’m afraid it was conny.

373
00:19:40,848 --> 00:19:42,783
( Emma sobbing )

374
00:19:45,052 --> 00:19:47,021
( Wailing )

375
00:19:47,054 --> 00:19:48,989
